import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import { IoIosArrowBack } from 'react-icons/io'

const CreateNote = () => {
  return (
    <section>
      <header className="create-note__header">
        <Link to="/" className="btn">
          <IoIosArrowBack />
        </Link>
        <button className="btn lg primary">
          Save
        </button>
      </header>
    </section>
  )
}

export default CreateNote
